  options:
  - optionText: "It wasn\u2019t easy\u2026 but I got the venom for you."
    replyText: "Heh, I can believe that. Those Goldrax bastards don\u2019t die easy.
      Thanks\u2026 now I can finally get rid of those hellish bugs. Here\u2019s 270
      dollars for your trouble."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 4
    questID: 45
    objectID: 255
    amountObject: 5
    actions:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 24aaf09396fe0444d8b00cb333eda2d5, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: aa313caeba89a64438952e344d2c8a14, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: e7da411a3b6752246a19e3e72488ed7a, type: 2}
  - optionText: "Looks like you\u2019ve got a lot of work here. How are you managing?"
    replyText: "Barely. Corn needs water, and my watering can\u2019s falling apart.
      Most of it leaks out before I even reach the field. Every day\u2019s a fight
      against weeds, heat, and busted tools. It\u2019s not easy, but at least my
      wife makes sure there\u2019s always a meal waiting for me at home. That\u2019s
      something, I guess."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: What do you do with all the corn you grow?
    replyText: My corn goes to the mill in Pinehill. They grind it into flour, and
      the bakery next door makes bread. But the road there is always a gamble - bandits
      or a broken wagon can delay everything. Luckily, they pay well once I deliver
      the goods.
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 0
    questID: 0
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions: []
  - optionText: Can I do anything else for you?
    replyText: "Actually\u2026 yeah. Corn beetles have been tearing through my field.
      I need to make a pesticide from Goldrax venom, but I\u2019m out of it. If you
      bring me 5 bottles, I\u2019d be grateful. I\u2019ll make sure you get paid
      well for it."
    nextNode: 1
    exitOption: 0
    conditionType: 1
    questID: 45
    objectID: 0
    amountObject: 0
    actions:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 693c6fb866bf06742aca36700cf2bbbc, type: 2}
  - optionText: Goodbye. Stay safe out there.
    replyText: 
